{"type": "article", "id": 32832, "title": "阿迪股价大涨，以及，草间弥生将在东京开最大个展 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-30T03:03:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 33379, "name": "Snapchat 滤镜"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 2114, "name": "Bottega Veneta"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 7124, "name": "草间弥生"}, {"id": 16286, "name": "Kendall Jenner"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/201609301023303Qx4sZh8rUzgVPjN.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/new-adidas-ceo-sets-off-in-pursuit-of-nike\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adidas </a>强势回归</b>&nbsp;| Adidas 重返世界第二运动品牌的位置。自  Kasper Rorsted 在今年一月担任 Adidas 的 CEO 以来，Adidas 重返世界第二运动品牌的位置，股价上涨了三分之二左右。Kasper Rorsted 称，Adidas 未来还面临着更大的挑战。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/ex-hugo-boss-chief-joins-bottega-veneta-as-ceo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Bottega Veneta 任命新的 CEO</b></a> | Claus-Dietrich Lahrs 成为 Bottega Veneta 新的 CEO，他曾担任 Hugo Boss 的 CEO，任期在今年的二月结束。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/daily-digest/2016/09/29#vetements-announces-new-recruit\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vetements 雇佣 Nina Nitsche 为新的时尚总监</b></a> | Nina Nitsche 此前在法国品牌 Maison Margiela 工作了二十余年。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/government-trade/asos-responds-criticism-factory-working-conditions-gmb-barnsley-10608810/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>ASOS 否认了对工厂工作环境的指控</b></a> | 此前，一个名为 GMB 的英国贸易协会组织指责 ASOS 剥削它在 Yorshire 工厂的工人。在 Buzzfeed News 介入此事之后，GMB 提出了对 ASOS 的指控。不过，ASOS 坚决否认了该指控。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/gap-x-gq\" rel=\"nofollow\">GAP 与 GQ 美国版第五次合作</a>，找了 4 家新晋男装设计师，推出了 2016 年限量合作的全明星阵容。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094235ndc0oRl6gXbqfhLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609300942350ntGTzqKs3jCgwLQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094235TrdNwQ9S3hlt86gf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094235nVSpY3FPgXTmR5aQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609300942354fSbeHMRABQidtP1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094235XDFk7MimxUlqt5OI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094235U2FZlyc7iSHued4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094236oJewKi4Mds2hASIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094236ds7wkFLOojqRnaSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094244JuFdVEzsA2yLvXRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/chanel-fw2016-handbags/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 发布了 2016 秋冬季的新款手袋</a>。今季还加入了一些特别的元素，比如 V 字手势和猫咪 emoji 等，Chanel 在试图变得幽默可爱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094253cT0xCjPil8g1KbZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094436yDn8dCheH14LuNqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094449in6lKptGr79gwNFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094449YqRvOZQxm1TjGl6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094450EayGCNXZ0DoVexF3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094450oU97LMm2WfNVtdrE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016093009445986EVrHQlcfpbdZtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094459QyRGgoX9WU12uMEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>草间弥生将在东京举办最大的个人展览 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/yayoi-kusama-my-eternal-soul-exhibition\" rel=\"nofollow\">《わが永远の魂》</a>。展览将展出超过 200 件作品，其中包括首度公开的 130 件作品。<br></p><p class=\"\">这个展览将于 2017 年 2 月 22 日至 5 月 22 日在日本东京国立新美术馆举行，并与 X-Girl 及 XLARGE 推出 2,000 套限定版预售门票套装，套装将附送联名 Tote Bag 一个，定价为 5,000 日元。另外还有附送南瓜匙扣的预售门票套装，定价为 3,000 日元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094542gPiAsUdRBJ5eKyXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094553Q3z6DK7k8ATrWve9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094601Uxcy3dO1wKMm9t8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Saucony Originals 与日本时尚名店 BILLY’S 合作，带来了一个名为 Nippon 的联名 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/saucony-originals-x-billys-grid-9000-nippon-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grid 9000</a> 系列。该系列将于 10 月 1 日正式发售，定价为 969 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094621arTZeAUQJl2W5pvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094623sxn8eYabfQmZrWqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094624GzwIbsOSFJ6l2Rdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Snapchat 越来越火，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/kendall-jenner-garage-magazine-cover/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kendall Jenner 以 Snapchat 滤镜造型</a>登上了 GARAGE 杂志，展现了她搞怪可爱的一面。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094716cWo6Iqhu215kt3Dl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930094716DO5cpTEwM1aG3ohP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609300947162vfKGS3CBQU1Y97W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609300947238AkKReWpYxyhPGQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609300947306YDVgy7hjUFviBz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}